  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Humam is a virtual reality (VR) application based on a set of interactive
    games that simulate real-life social situations in a safe and structured way.
    The app aims to help individuals who experience social anxiety by placing them
    in virtual scenarios that resemble everyday situations, such as talking to strangers,
    ordering coffee, or giving a presentation in front of an audience.\n\nThese games
    gradually increase in difficulty and provide step-by-step exposure to anxiety-provoking
    situations, helping users build confidence and develop communication and social
    interaction skills. HUMAM also tracks physiological indicators to adjust the
    level of challenge within the game according to the player\u2019s condition,
    making the experience personalized and more effective.\n\nIn addition, individuals
    who do not suffer from social anxiety can benefit from HUMAM as a training platform
    to enhance communication skills, improve performance in social situations, and
    increase confidence in public speaking."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: e3fc4e1ee537a604baf1fa921290eb32, type: 2}
